, \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H\\u00e9ctor_Beller\\u00edn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H\\u00e9ctor_Beller\\u00edn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a London-based fashion stylist\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1644}, {\"ngram\": \"lots\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1661}, {\"ngram\": \"sportspeople\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1677}, {\"ngram\": \"the sports kit\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1796}, {\"ngram\": \"the 'fit\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1818}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'From the sci-fi-coded pistol and glasses, to the monochrome Fila two-piece, as well as the silver rings and elephant keyring, Yeji's outfit is cyberpunk heroine meets underground club kid, all with a personal touch.\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 2064, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1909, \"end\": 1913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fila\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fila\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fila\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fila\"}, {\"begin\": 1975, \"end\": 1979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Itzy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0797352658170626e-17, \"text\": \"Yeji\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Itzy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Itzy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sci-fi-coded pistol\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1877}, {\"ngram\": \"glasses\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1889}, {\"ngram\": \"cyberpunk heroine\", \"from\": 1992, \"to\": 2009}, {\"ngram\": \"underground club kid\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2036}, {\"ngram\": \"a personal touch\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2063}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Even the way she wears her ponytail through her baseball cap is cool.\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2136, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her ponytail\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2102}, {\"ngram\": \"her baseball cap\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2127}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All in all, it's a very good outfit, which I am sure will secure her a fashion campaign or two, once the Games are over.'\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2258, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very good outfit\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2172}, {\"ngram\": \"a fashion campaign\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2224}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2247}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, previous footage of Kim has emerged, also highlighting the shooter's style - this time, showing her gold-winning appearance at the International Shooting Sport Federation World Cup held in Baku, Azerbaijan in May.\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2285, \"end\": 2288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 1.725943187715797e-12, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}, {\"begin\": 2396, \"end\": 2435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Shooting_Sport_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Shooting Sport Federation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Shooting_Sport_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Shooting_Sport_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 2436, \"end\": 2445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA_World_Cup\", \"score\": 0.9999512195510799, \"rank\": 2.695739601332121e-05, \"text\": \"World Cup\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA_World_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA_World_Cup\"}, {\"begin\": 2454, \"end\": 2458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baku\", \"score\": 0.9999930932974392, \"rank\": 6.906750038484616e-06, \"text\": \"Baku\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbp